      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   m-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mmessg"
                                         using m                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se errore : uscita                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
            if       m-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to exe-pgm-frg-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
