                     go to exe-pgm-frg-400.
           move      "PT"                 to   b-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mbckgr"
                                         using b                      .
           go to     exe-pgm-frg-200.
       exe-pgm-frg-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
