           move      w-cnt-stp-cod-mod    to   r-fix-cod-mod          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo modulo                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-stp-tip-mod    to   r-fix-tip-mod          .
