           move      v-dat                to   rr-dat-min             .
       acc-dat-min-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data a zero non accettabile                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-dat-min           =    zero
                     go to acc-dat-min-100.
