           move      rr-dat-min           to   w-ese-cge-dtr          .
           perform   det-ese-cge-000      thru det-ese-cge-999        .
           move      w-ese-cge-esa        to   w-stp-ese-ini          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test di congruenza tra data minima e mas-   *
      *                  * sima                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-dat-max           =    zero
                     go to  acc-dat-min-600.
           if        w-stp-ese-ini        =    w-stp-ese-fin
                     go to  acc-dat-min-600.
